569
00:40:48,000 --> 00:40:49,670
since she couldn't see you before she left.

570
00:40:51,440 --> 00:40:55,140
That moron. All she did was work nonstop.

571
00:41:25,770 --> 00:41:26,880
Jung Hee.

572
00:41:27,980 --> 00:41:31,750
I wanted to see you before I left,

573
00:41:32,610 --> 00:41:33,950
but I just left.

574
00:41:35,920 --> 00:41:38,890
I was happy living with my kind...

575
00:41:39,250 --> 00:41:41,020
and pretty Jung Hee.

576
00:41:42,290 --> 00:41:43,320
That's right.

577
00:41:43,830 --> 00:41:46,900
I left you a gift in the closet.

578
00:41:49,630 --> 00:41:51,400
I made it.

579
00:41:52,670 --> 00:41:54,400
I hope you like it.

580
00:42:00,080 --> 00:42:01,140
Jung Hee.

581
00:42:02,980 --> 00:42:05,180
Grow up to be a beautiful girl.

582
00:42:05,710 --> 00:42:06,950
Be proud.

583
00:42:08,480 --> 00:42:09,750
Love, Auntie.

584
00:42:55,230 --> 00:42:56,730
Are you leaving?

585
00:42:57,000 --> 00:42:58,170
Why did you come again?

586
00:42:58,830 --> 00:43:01,740
Everyone knows me in this neighborhood.

587
00:43:02,670 --> 00:43:03,870
It's hard for me to make a living.

588
00:43:05,070 --> 00:43:06,410
Take care of yourself.

589
00:43:08,080 --> 00:43:10,350
I already told you.

590
00:43:12,480 --> 00:43:14,450
How can you do this to me?

591
00:43:15,450 --> 00:43:17,090
I heard you were expelled from school.

592
00:43:19,690 --> 00:43:21,990
How far will you go until you wake up?

593
00:43:26,690 --> 00:43:28,300
Forget about me...

594
00:43:29,830 --> 00:43:31,170
and have a good life.

595
00:43:36,400 --> 00:43:37,510
I will.

596
00:43:38,340 --> 00:43:40,380
If that's what you want,

597
00:43:40,880 --> 00:43:41,940
I will.

598
00:43:45,310 --> 00:43:47,080
I'm not confident,

599
00:43:48,020 --> 00:43:49,680
but I'll try.

600
00:44:32,090 --> 00:44:33,330
How will you live?

601
00:44:35,000 --> 00:44:36,330
It doesn't matter...

602
00:44:36,900 --> 00:44:38,600
to you anymore.

603
00:44:43,770 --> 00:44:44,870
Are you sure...

604
00:44:46,270 --> 00:44:47,440
you won't regret it?

605
00:44:48,910 --> 00:44:50,850
Won't you regret taking off with me?

606
00:44:51,350 --> 00:44:53,420
Why would I when I'm with you?

607
00:44:54,820 --> 00:44:56,850
If I'm with you,

608
00:44:57,620 --> 00:44:58,890
why would I?

609
00:45:22,340 --> 00:45:24,650
Don't leave me behind.

610
00:45:28,680 --> 00:45:30,150
Don't leave me.

611
00:45:35,420 --> 00:45:36,790
I love you, Hae Joo.

612
00:45:53,340 --> 00:45:54,340
Okay.

613
00:46:01,020 --> 00:46:02,620
Give it to me.

614
00:46:06,290 --> 00:46:07,490
Let's go, Eng Cho.

615
00:46:10,190 --> 00:46:12,430
Sit at the front with Eng Cho.

616
00:46:12,430 --> 00:46:14,130
I'll sit here.

617
00:46:15,060 --> 00:46:16,830
I'll sit here too.

618
00:46:20,140 --> 00:46:21,140
It's finished.

619
00:46:21,140 --> 00:46:23,070
Okay. Thanks.

620
00:46:23,300 --> 00:46:25,240
- Thank you.
- I appreciate it.

621
00:46:26,910 --> 00:46:29,710
Hae Joo. When you settle down,

622
00:46:30,080 --> 00:46:31,150
make sure to contact me.

623
00:46:31,150 --> 00:46:32,410
Of course.

624
00:46:33,150 --> 00:46:34,350
Hey,

625
00:46:34,420 --> 00:46:36,180
you better be good to Hae Joo.

626
00:46:36,180 --> 00:46:37,850
I'll be watching you.

627
00:46:37,850 --> 00:46:40,220
I'm so scared of you.

628
00:46:43,530 --> 00:46:44,530
Don't worry.

629
00:46:45,630 --> 00:46:47,030
I'll take good care of her.

630
00:46:55,270 --> 00:46:56,370
Take care.

631
00:47:01,410 --> 00:47:04,080
Thank you, my friend.

632
00:47:14,520 --> 00:47:16,190
- We're leaving.
- Okay.

633
00:47:21,930 --> 00:47:23,330
Don't get sick.

634
00:47:23,900 --> 00:47:25,030
Stay healthy.

635
00:47:58,530 --> 00:47:59,700
Stop crying.

636
00:48:00,770 --> 00:48:02,070
Hae Joo will be fine.

637
00:48:03,140 --> 00:48:04,240
I'm not crying.

638
00:48:05,910 --> 00:48:07,180
I know that.

639
00:48:07,980 --> 00:48:09,510
Hae Joo will be fine.

640
00:48:12,280 --> 00:48:13,280
Park Hae Joo.

641
00:48:13,550 --> 00:48:15,620
It was her dream...

642
00:48:15,750 --> 00:48:16,990
to fall in a passionate love.

643
00:48:18,420 --> 00:48:19,550
Her dream came true.

644
00:48:20,990 --> 00:48:22,060
What about you?

645
00:48:22,860 --> 00:48:24,230
What was your dream?

646
00:48:28,100 --> 00:48:29,160
Son Jin?

647
00:48:29,900 --> 00:48:31,370
You little...

648
00:48:32,630 --> 00:48:34,340
You little...

649
00:48:36,240 --> 00:48:37,740
Since you're feeling down,

650
00:48:38,210 --> 00:48:40,980
should we go see a movie?

651
00:48:41,780 --> 00:48:44,380
Today's show would be sold out already.

652
00:48:44,380 --> 00:48:45,550
It's Sunday.

653
00:48:46,180 --> 00:48:48,650
I already got us tickets.

654
00:48:50,720 --> 00:48:53,460
Wow. Bae Dong Moon.

655
00:48:53,790 --> 00:48:54,920
Also,

656
00:48:55,420 --> 00:48:58,260
I'm going to start officially.

657
00:48:58,360 --> 00:48:59,460
Start what?

658
00:49:02,030 --> 00:49:03,430
Being your boyfriend.

659
00:49:05,230 --> 00:49:06,270
This is...

660
00:49:06,630 --> 00:49:09,340
considered the first step.

661
00:49:10,170 --> 00:49:11,370
Who says?

662
00:49:12,210 --> 00:49:13,210
Bye.

663
00:49:16,110 --> 00:49:18,710
Anyway, if you show up,

664
00:49:19,050 --> 00:49:20,620
I'll consider that you agree.

665
00:49:20,820 --> 00:49:22,120
I'll become your boyfriend.

666
00:49:22,820 --> 00:49:24,420
Go away.

667
00:49:26,960 --> 00:49:29,060
See you later, Jung Hee.

668
00:49:43,640 --> 00:49:45,710
Who says you can be my boyfriend?

669
00:49:49,280 --> 00:49:50,280
Jung Hee.

670
00:49:52,980 --> 00:49:54,020
Jin.

671
00:49:54,750 --> 00:49:56,350
What are you doing here?

672
00:49:56,790 --> 00:49:58,820
Oh. Well...

673
00:49:58,820 --> 00:50:01,060
What do we do?

674
00:50:01,060 --> 00:50:02,820
Hae Joo already left.

675
00:50:03,490 --> 00:50:04,560
Really?

676
00:50:05,990 --> 00:50:08,200
Did she leave today?

677
00:50:10,400 --> 00:50:11,500
I didn't know.

678
00:50:15,640 --> 00:50:16,640
Did the move...

679
00:50:17,540 --> 00:50:18,640
go well?

680
00:50:19,310 --> 00:50:20,310
Yes.

681
00:50:21,080 --> 00:50:23,010
Well... Then...

682
00:50:23,510 --> 00:50:25,550
Did you come on family business?

683
00:50:26,150 --> 00:50:27,150
I...

684
00:50:28,180 --> 00:50:29,380
missed you.

685
00:50:31,950 --> 00:50:33,760
I came because I missed you.

686
00:50:36,290 --> 00:50:38,890
But it's already getting late.

687
00:50:39,560 --> 00:50:40,630
What should I do?

688
00:50:40,960 --> 00:50:42,930
Did you wait a long time?

689
00:50:43,300 --> 00:50:46,100
I was helping Hae Joo with her move.

690
00:50:46,130 --> 00:50:47,270
Did you?

691
00:50:48,140 --> 00:50:49,300
Good job.

692
00:51:01,180 --> 00:51:02,580
For some reason,

693
00:51:04,350 --> 00:51:06,350
I kept thinking about you while in Seoul.

694
00:51:07,060 --> 00:51:08,520
Then I realized...

695
00:51:10,390 --> 00:51:11,460
that I...

696
00:51:12,960 --> 00:51:15,860
started to like you.

697
00:51:20,400 --> 00:51:21,440
Jung Hee.

698
00:51:23,240 --> 00:51:24,570
If it's not too late,

699
00:51:26,510 --> 00:51:30,080
will you accept my feelings?

700
00:51:35,350 --> 00:51:36,380
Were you surprised?

701
00:51:37,320 --> 00:51:38,490
I'm sure you are.

702
00:51:43,630 --> 00:51:45,490
I have to drop by home.

703
00:51:46,900 --> 00:51:48,660
I have a ticket for the bus at 4pm.

704
00:51:49,400 --> 00:51:52,400
Can I see you before I go?

705
00:51:56,340 --> 00:51:57,670
The 4pm bus?

706
00:51:59,740 --> 00:52:01,910
I'll wait for you at the terminal.

707
00:52:07,380 --> 00:52:09,650
(Showtime: 4pm)

708
00:52:10,150 --> 00:52:12,520
Why does everything...

709
00:52:12,950 --> 00:52:15,190
come to you a step too late?

710
00:53:53,860 --> 00:53:54,960
Jung Hee.

711
00:53:58,430 --> 00:53:59,490
I'm sorry.

712
00:54:01,930 --> 00:54:05,070
The film is starting. Please come in.

713
00:54:27,320 --> 00:54:30,630
The 4pm bus to Seoul is
departing soon. Get on.

714
00:54:48,280 --> 00:54:49,310
Jung Hee.

715
00:55:03,830 --> 00:55:05,060
Aren't you going in?

716
00:55:05,490 --> 00:55:07,900
- Pardon?
- It's starting soon.

717
00:55:28,850 --> 00:55:32,090
Jung Hee. Are you not coming?

718
00:55:33,350 --> 00:55:34,990
I guess you don't like me.

719
00:56:21,470 --> 00:56:22,570
Is this...

720
00:56:23,870 --> 00:56:25,170
how it's going to end?

721
00:56:25,740 --> 00:56:28,740
What are you doing? The film is over.

722
00:56:30,040 --> 00:56:32,380
I'm leaving.

723
00:56:33,110 --> 00:56:34,480
I'll leave.

724
00:56:37,620 --> 00:56:38,620
Jung Hee.

725
00:56:40,290 --> 00:56:42,660
Dong Moon. Is that where you were?

726
00:56:48,530 --> 00:56:49,560
Jung Hee.

727
00:56:53,940 --> 00:56:54,970
When did you get here?

728
00:56:55,040 --> 00:56:57,140
I was a little late,

729
00:56:57,440 --> 00:56:59,440
so I couldn't find my seat and sat here.

730
00:56:59,540 --> 00:57:00,980
My neck hurts.

731
00:57:04,650 --> 00:57:05,780
Jung Hee.

732
00:57:07,620 --> 00:57:08,780
Thank you.

733
00:57:14,620 --> 00:57:16,090
Thank you so much.

734
00:57:17,390 --> 00:57:19,930
What's wrong with you? Let me go.

735
00:57:29,940 --> 00:57:30,970
Jung Hee.

736
00:57:34,310 --> 00:57:35,380
Bae Dong Moon.

737
00:57:37,010 --> 00:57:38,150
You won.

738
00:57:51,160 --> 00:57:54,130
I thought you weren't coming.

739
00:57:56,330 --> 00:57:57,770
Why wouldn't I?

740
00:57:58,100 --> 00:57:59,570
It'd be a waste of a movie ticket.

741
00:58:00,470 --> 00:58:02,140
Is that why you came?

742
00:58:03,240 --> 00:58:04,610
Didn't you come for me?

743
00:58:06,240 --> 00:58:07,280
No.

744
00:58:11,310 --> 00:58:12,350
You did.

745
00:58:15,680 --> 00:58:16,920
Then...

746
00:58:19,690 --> 00:58:21,490
Well...

747
00:58:22,960 --> 00:58:25,930
I started to like Dong Moon.

748
00:58:29,160 --> 00:58:32,030
I'm sorry, Jin.

749
00:58:34,900 --> 00:58:36,140
Don't be sorry.

750
00:58:37,810 --> 00:58:39,410
People...

751
00:58:40,610 --> 00:58:42,140
change minds all the time.

752
00:58:45,250 --> 00:58:46,380
Just like...

753
00:58:47,150 --> 00:58:48,220
how my heart...

754
00:58:49,750 --> 00:58:51,290
turned towards you.

755
00:59:03,260 --> 00:59:04,430
Right?

756
00:59:06,270 --> 00:59:09,040
No. I really didn't.

757
00:59:11,070 --> 00:59:12,140
You're...

758
00:59:12,970 --> 00:59:14,510
giving me the permission, right?

759
00:59:15,210 --> 00:59:16,750
As your boyfriend?

760
00:59:18,980 --> 00:59:21,120
- Maybe.
- What do you mean maybe?

761
00:59:22,250 --> 00:59:24,250
I can see it on your face.

762
00:59:25,020 --> 00:59:26,890
Nothing is on my face.

763
00:59:28,960 --> 00:59:30,060
It's written all over.

764
00:59:30,390 --> 00:59:32,390
"Yes, let's do that."

765
00:59:32,890 --> 00:59:34,230
That's what it says.

766
00:59:35,360 --> 00:59:36,600
You're a liar.

767
00:59:44,110 --> 00:59:46,170
Hey, Dong Moon.

768
00:59:48,980 --> 00:59:50,110
Jung Hee.

769
00:59:54,820 --> 00:59:56,550
I really, really like you.

770
01:00:18,070 --> 01:00:19,210
Jung Hee.

771
01:00:27,920 --> 01:00:29,250
Wait for me.

772
01:00:29,520 --> 01:00:30,620
I don't want to.

773
01:00:30,990 --> 01:00:33,350
- Let's walk together.
- I don't want to.

774
01:00:34,090 --> 01:00:36,060
Don't be mad. Come on.

775
01:00:36,220 --> 01:00:37,290
All right.

776
01:00:38,190 --> 01:00:40,030
- Do you want steamed bun?
- Steamed buns?

777
01:00:40,100 --> 01:00:42,030
Yes. No?

778
01:00:50,870 --> 01:00:52,170
Eun Ja,

779
01:00:52,940 --> 01:00:54,640
- I love you.
- Are you crazy?

780
01:00:54,640 --> 01:00:55,680
I love you.

781
01:00:55,680 --> 01:00:56,880
- I'm crazy about you.
- What are you saying?

782
01:00:56,880 --> 01:00:59,810
Roses? Daisies? You look like them all.

783
01:00:59,810 --> 01:01:01,650
- I'll tattle to Jung Hee.
- Go ahead!

784
01:01:01,650 --> 01:01:02,850
What's wrong?

785
01:01:07,420 --> 01:01:08,520
Suk Hee.

786
01:01:19,630 --> 01:01:20,770
Please take them.

787
01:01:31,610 --> 01:01:35,780
(Thank you for watching
Girls' Generation 1979.)

788
01:01:39,120 --> 01:01:40,490
Please be happy,

789
01:01:40,960 --> 01:01:42,190
Young Choon.

790
01:02:12,550 --> 01:02:13,920
What is this?

791
01:02:15,620 --> 01:02:18,060
Come over here! Do this again.

792
01:02:19,160 --> 01:02:20,700
How many times is this?

793
01:02:21,530 --> 01:02:23,160
I told you to do it properly!

794
01:02:23,160 --> 01:02:26,600
Ever since I became a young breadwinner,

795
01:02:26,840 --> 01:02:28,970
I never worked like you.

796
01:02:29,800 --> 01:02:31,740
How many times did I tell you?

797
01:02:31,740 --> 01:02:32,910
Hey!

798
01:02:33,580 --> 01:02:34,580
Seriously!

799
01:02:35,540 --> 01:02:37,580
Let's do it right!

800
01:02:37,850 --> 01:02:40,920
What is this? Look at that.
